Package: IMComplete
Type: Package
Title: An end-to-end pipeline for IMC analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Oscar Dong
Maintainer: Oscar Dong <oscardong4@gmail.com>
Description: IMComplete provides a comprehensive and automated pipeline for 
    analyzing Imaging Mass Cytometry (IMC) data. It enables efficient preprocessing, 
    visualisation, and annotation of IMC datasets, with functionalities for 
    batch correction, dimensionality reduction, clustering, and marker expression 
    analysis. The package is designed for both novice and advanced users, offering 
    user-friendly defaults while allowing detailed customization.
